#. module: community_parcel
#: model:mail.template,body_html:community_parcel.mail_template_parcel_arrival
msgid ""
"<div style=\"margin:0;padding:0;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\">\n"
"    <p>親愛的 {{ object.unit_id.display_name }} 住戶您好，</p>\n"
"    <p>您有一件包裹已送達社區管理室，詳細資訊如下：</p>\n"
"    <table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;margin:10px 0;\">\n"
"        <tr>\n"
"            <td style=\"padding:4px 12px 4px 0;font-weight:bold;\">編號</td>\n"
"            <td style=\"padding:4px 0;\">{{ object.name }}</td>\n"
"        </tr>\n"
"        <tr>\n"
"            <td style=\"padding:4px 12px 4px 0;font-weight:bold;\">類型</td>\n"
"            <td style=\"padding:4px 0;\">{{ object.type_id.name or '未分類' }}</td>\n"
"        </tr>\n"
"        <tr>\n"
"            <td style=\"padding:4px 12px 4px 0;font-weight:bold;\">條碼</td>\n"
"            <td style=\"padding:4px 0;\">{{ object.barcode or '無' }}</td>\n"
"        </tr>\n"
"        <tr>\n"
"            <td style=\"padding:4px 12px 4px 0;font-weight:bold;\">收件時間</td>\n"
"            <td style=\"padding:4px 0;\">{{ object.received_date }}</td>\n"
"        </tr>\n"
"        <tr>\n"
"            <td style=\"padding:4px 12px 4px 0;font-weight:bold;\">管理室</td>\n"
"            <td style=\"padding:4px 0;\">{{ object.office_id.name or '未指定' }}</td>\n"
"        </tr>\n"
"    </table>\n"
"    <p>請盡快至管理室領取，謝謝！</p>\n"
"</div>\n"
"            "
